<ext_description linkend="External_functional_model_arm.External_functional_model">
An <b>External_functional_model</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="function_based_behaviour_representation:arm:Function_based_behaviour_representation_arm.Functional_model" />
where an external digital file contains the model. 
<note>This requires us to have at least one <express_ref linkend="function_based_behaviour_representation:arm:Function_based_behaviour_representation_arm.Functional_representation_item" />, which should represent the top level function being definied in the external file.</note>
</ext_description>
